longBusinessSummary: Safello Group AB (publ) provides a brokerage platform for individuals and businesses. The company operates its platform, which enables the buying and selling of cryptocurrencies, such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, and various digital assets; and the storing, swapping, transferring, and receiving of crypto assets. It offers its services through Safello Mobile and Safello Web App. Safello Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
